This EULA applies to any software, script, or plugin that includes the Tool and bears this notice.
Any user, whether an individual, corporation, or other organization, shall be deemed to have agreed to this Agreement upon purchasing, downloading, installing, copying, using, or modifying the Tool.
If you do not agree to this Agreement, you may not use the Tool.

